<P>__{(whispering loudly)}
<D>__{look toby, the guys in that movie are not 28 year old file clerks who live with their grandmothers in an ethnic ghetto.}
<C>__{joyce}
<D>__{that's enough, harvey.}
<C>__{harvey}
<D>__{they didn't get their computers like you did by trading in a bunch of box tops and $49.50 at the supermarket.}
<A>__{joyce folds her arms in disapproval. toby starts to laugh.}
